OL,3,CCalls to scrap trans inclusion
OL,4,Cguidance criticised as 'political'
OL,6,FA Jersey politician is calling for
OL,7,Fguidance around transgender inclusion
OL,8,Fin schools to be revoked - a move that
OL,9,Fthe Education Minister has hit back at
OL,10,Fas "appearing politically driven
OL,11,Frather than grounded in evidence".
OL,13,FThe 'Treating Children as Children'
OL,14,Fproposition, lodged by Deputy Sir
OL,15,FPhilip Bailhache, argues that existing
OL,16,Fguidance does not reflect the findings
OL,17,Fof The 2024 Cass Review.
