OL,3,CCalls to scrap trans inclusion
OL,4,Cguidance criticised as 'political'
OL,6,FThe report by Dr Hilary Cass -
OL,7,Fcommissioned by NHS England - looked
OL,8,Fat gender identity services for under-
OL,9,F18s, following a rise in NHS referrals
OL,10,Ffrom young people questioning their
OL,11,Fgender.
OL,13,FDeputy Bailhache believes Jersey's
OL,14,Fexisting guidance is "muddled" and
OL,15,F"contradictory" and follows the
OL,16,F"gender affirmative" approach - a
OL,17,Fmodel of care that accepts an
OL,18,Findividual's self-identified gender.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/12
