OL,6,FIt also provides clear guidance on how
OL,7,Fto identify and report transphobic
OL,8,Fbullying, alongside the requirement
OL,9,Ffor schools to provide a gender
OL,10,Fneutral toilet option, where necessary.
OL,12,FThe CYPES guidance also recognises
OL,13,Fthat coming out is "a hugely
OL,14,Fsignificant step in any LGBTQ+
OL,15,Fperson's journey" and advises seeking
OL,16,Fpermission from the child before
OL,17,Fsharing the disclosure further.
