OL,6,FJersey's Education Minister has
OL,7,Fcriticised proposals to revoke
OL,8,Fguidance around transgender inclusion
OL,9,Fin schools as "appearing politically
OL,10,Fdriven".
OL,12,FDeputy Rob Ward argues that the
OL,13,Fexisting trans inclusion guidance is
OL,14,F"evidenceinformed, nonstatutory, and
OL,15,Ffocused on pupil welfare".
