OL,6,FHe adds: "I would like to raise
OL,7,Fserious concerns about the
OL,8,Fproposition's implications for
OL,9,Fsafeguarding practice, professional
OL,10,Fintegrity, and Jersey's statutory
OL,11,Fframeworks.
OL,13,F"The current Trans Inclusion Guidance,
OL,14,Fpublished in March 2025, was developed
OL,15,Fto help schools navigate complex
OL,16,Fsituations with clarity and
OL,17,Fsensitivity.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/12
