OL,6,F"Jersey law is clear: children and
OL,7,Fyoung people have the right to
OL,8,Fparticipate in decisions that affect
OL,9,Fthem, and policies must be rooted in
OL,10,Fnon-discrimination, dignity, and
OL,11,Frespect.
OL,13,F"Safeguarding must be led by
OL,14,Fprofessionals - not politics."
